BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Bike to School Week
DTSTART:20260601T110000Z
DTEND:20260605T210000Z
DTSTAMP:20260505T062702Z
UID:c576f8ab-3a84-52db-a8d0-273df3d4a213
DESCRIPTION:Register your school for Bike to School Week 2026!\n\nCommunit
 ies that embrace active school travel help their kids lead healthier lifes
 tyles and improve their school performance\, while also reducing traffic a
 nd pollution and making school zones safer for vulnerable road users. Also
 \, being able to bike to school with your friends is just plain fun.\n\nSc
 hools in Ontario are encouraged to register for Bike to School Week using 
 the form below and receive a suite of resources and materials to help orga
 nize bike-friendly events in a school environment.\n\n(https://www.bikemon
 th.ca/biketoschoolweek) REGISTER HERE\nURL: https://www.cycleto.ca/bike_to
 _school_week
LOCATION:
URL:https://www.cycleto.ca/bike_to_school_week
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
