DESCRIPTION:Bike to Work Day is back!\n\nBike to Work Day Group Commute is
  on Thursday\, June 4. This event\, organized in collaboration with the Ci
 ty of Toronto\, has traditionally been the kick off event for Bike Month t
 hat has seen over a thousand commuters join Cycle Toronto and Bike Month p
 artners on a morning group commute to Nathan Phillips Square.\n\nDetails a
 bout start times & locations are coming soon\, so be sure to check back he
 re or RSVP!\nURL: https://www.cycleto.ca/bike_to_work_day_2026
LOCATION:Nathan Phillips Square\n100 Queen St W\nToronto ON M5H 2N1\nCA
